column5: Added object-fit, object-position to vendor property list

Fix boxModel parameter

.replace() only replaces the first occurence of "&" in css.bm, so box-sizing only worked for the -moz prefix.

Fixed IE8 Fallback

The for ... in loop shouldn't be used for arrays. On IE8 "a[k]" didn't only return strings, which meant trouble when calling ".charAt".
